data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bath ranch with gem offers an array of exceptional features designed to enhance your comfort and convenience. Nestled in desirable Paint Brush Hills, this property boasts numerous upgrades and energy-saving amenities that make it a true standout. The well-appointed kitchen with granite countertops and a double oven is perfect for cooking and entertaining. The primary bedroom with adjoining bathroom boasts double vanity with granite counters, and two spacious closets. A wet bar in the basement adds an element of entertainment and relaxation, making it an ideal space for gatherings. Say goodbye to soaring electricity bills! This home comes equipped with solar panels that not only reduce your carbon footprint but also provide substantial savings on your monthly electric expenses. Enjoy a tranquil atmosphere and protect your furniture from harmful UV rays with the UV protection and noise-reducing windows installed throughout the rear of the house. Entertain guests with a stylish bar featuring hanging moon lights. Relax and breathtaking mountain views from the backyard, providing a serene and picturesque atmosphere on the deck and cement patio. This meticulously maintained home offers a harmonious blend of modern amenities and thoughtful upgrades, making it the perfect place to call home. Schedule a viewing today and start envisioning your future in this exceptional home!
